Can everyone do a split?

After how long is it possible to do a split? Anyone can do a split, but not everyone has the persistence and desine to do it. 
The keys to success are, of course, regular stretching and a large dose of persistence.

Some people will be able to do painless and technically correct splits after just a few weeks, others will take half a year and others maybe a whole year.
